name: Weird days.
description:
There was a point, a point in my life where I was only an observer, it was after the rise, after the fall, after the upheavals, after the funeral.
There was a point in my life where I no longer had to cry, or laugh, or be happy, or be euphoric, where I began to live with all my problems, my pain, my ghosts and my fears.
I saw them walk by my side, I saw them speak, I felt how they touched my shoulders, how they whispered in my ear, how they laughed at me ...
It felt so good ...
